cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.SY

The paper discusses the development of a benchmark set of tasks for evaluating multitask learning in continuous domains. This involves the use of reinforcement learning algorithms and OpenAI Gym, which are commonly associated with the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), computer vision (cs.CV), and systems and control (cs.SY). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
